Class BackgroundAnimationGameState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.cooperroalson.untitled_thinggy_thingg.core.drawing.sprites.TextureSprite

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sprite, GameState, java.io.Serializable

    public class BackgroundAnimationGameState
extends AnimationSprite
implements GameState
    An implementation of GameState that extends AnimationSprite, and simply displays an animation. Designed to be used as a background for a UIGameState.
